# Low-Poly BR — PvP + PvE (StackBlitz-ready)

Runs 100% in the browser via **StackBlitz WebContainers**. Uses Colyseus + the **standard WebSocket transport** (pure JS) compatible with WebContainers.

## ▶️ Run on StackBlitz
1. Open StackBlitz and **drag & drop** this unzipped folder into the editor.
2. It auto-installs and **auto-runs** via `.stackblitzrc` (`npm run dev`).
3. Open the preview → click **PLAY PvP (32)** or **PLAY PvE (32)**.

## Manual commands (if needed)

```bash
npm install --legacy-peer-deps
npm run dev
```

## Notes
- WebContainers block native Node addons, so we use `@colyseus/ws-transport` (pure JS).
- Client SDK connects with an **HTTP** base (matchmaking) then upgrades to WebSocket.
